Package org.bluezoo.gumdrop.servlet.jsp

Interface JSPElement

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractJSPElement, CommentElement, CustomTagElement, DeclarationElement, DirectiveElement, ExpressionElement, ScriptletElement, StandardActionElement, TextElement
    public interface JSPElement
    Base interface for all JSP elements in the abstract syntax tree. JSP elements represent the various components that make up a JSP page, including text content, scriptlets, expressions, declarations, and directives.

    All JSP elements maintain location information for error reporting and debugging purposes.

    Author:
    Chris Burdess
